OL,2,MUsing the railway network as a flatbed
OL,4,Mscanner
OL,6,CPhilomena Gray
OL,7,CFri 20:20-20:50
OL,8,CStage A
OL,10,GI've been taking extremely wide photos
OL,11,Gby pointing an industrial linear
OL,12,Gcamera out the window of a moving
OL,13,Gtrain and stitching together the
OL,14,Gseveral thousand lines captured per
OL,15,Gsecond after the fact. I'll talk about
OL,16,Gthe pains of measuring the speed and
OL,17,Gcollecting each line fast enough to
OL,18,Gproduce a coherent image, as well as
OL,19,Gthe problems of processing and
OL,20,Gdisplaying such wide images.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
